{"tid":1443401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Set Deadline好撚重要","createTime":"2019-08-11T08:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:35:08.000Z","uid":22607,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a25338bbb6edebd0e2f70bd87fdc8ec11937226c","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"成場運動行到宜家，我相信大家都開始諗可以點繼續<br />\n係8.5之後，我地就冇set過任何deadline比政府<br />\n只係四出遊擊，打唔到政府嘅七寸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我覺得deadline係好重要<br />\n一黎係可以預告比市民聽我地會升級行動，出師有名<br />\n二黎係可以確立返我地自己嘅行動目標同意義，對準政權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇<br />\n以下開放行動升級同set deadline討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f645ecccdf449e2212f7705f549307d53c0b0014","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:16:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f4895a5c96e6572b1944ec028a7388d213a24ae","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"442b74fcb62985a72873021578c87cc00c643a4d","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:16:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5846626b59fe41f1b80acc3cc46467154e0c337","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c4a174a2c0f095462a38b8ae8224158f8a8a6ec","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"405f42d8954e46284e99fc969c9ec3f9f5c102e1","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa944033871e9785a45213a0ea5c4d07afe43300","tid":1443401,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:17:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efeb96e0b78ba2705b0a90c36d3635456c772128","tid":1443401,"uid"